							SERVICES
							<AudioLinesIcon class="inline-block ml-2 w-4 h-4 text-red-600" />
						</h2>
					</div>

					<div class="top-20 z-10 sticky pt-10">
						<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 bg-black p-6 rounded-2xl w-full h-120">
							<div class="flex flex-col gap-8 col-span-1 px-8 py-6 rounded-3xl">
								<h3 class="font-semibold text-2xl uppercase">Music <br />Production</h3>
								
								<svg width="16" height="8" viewBox="0 0 16 8" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
									<line x1="7" y1="1" x2="1" y2="1" stroke="#EC003F" stroke-opacity="0.88" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
									<line x1="15" y1="7" x2="1" y2="7" stroke="#EC003F" stroke-opacity="0.88" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
								</svg>
								
								<p class="font-light text-gray-400 text-xl leading-relaxed">
									I create and shape your music from concept to final product, ensuring every element is polished and impactful.
								</p>
							</div>
							<img class="col-span-1 bg-zinc-900 rounded-lg h-108" src={placeholder1.src} alt="Placeholder" />
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="top-30 z-20 sticky grid md:grid-cols-2 bg-black p-6 rounded-2xl w-full h-120">
