							Crafting sonic landscapes. <br>Building cultural moments.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<hr class="border-white/5 border-t">

				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3">
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-6 col-span-1">
						<!--
						RATIONAL
						Fiverr: 45
						Spotify: 73 rock 47 acoustic 19 others
						Total: 184
