						<SendIcon class="w-40 h-40 text-red-600" />
					</div>
					
					<h2 class="font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-tighter">Let's Work <span class="text-rose-600">Together</span></h2>
					<p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
						To request a quote or ask questions, reach out directly via Instagram, Whatsapp or e-mail.
